metadata.name: Tis My Season
metadata.description:
A nostalgic piece filled with dreams and wishes.  
 The colors of innocence and possibility blending together in a beautiful dreamscape. A time of imaginative thought, manifested in words and images, capturing the rare and fleeting moments of joy and hope using a playful array of shapes and figures adorning the canvas, giving off a whimsical and joyous vibe emphasizing the power of reverie and imagination.
